      <title>特朗普捐款人支付 25,000 美元在 Zoom 上向道格·伯古姆提问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/trump-donors-pay-25-000-to-ask-doug-burgum-questions-on-zoom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的捐赠者支付了 25,000 美元，在一次虚拟筹款活动中向北达科他州州长道格·伯格姆提出一个问题——他是共和党候选人竞选搭档的热门候选人之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/trump-donors-pay-25-000-to-ask-doug-burgum-questions-on-zoom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 17:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登与特朗普对峙，电动汽车、芯片、加密货币股票成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/ev-chips-crypto-stocks-in-cross-hairs-as-biden-trump-face-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市基本摆脱了 11 月美国大选带来的不确定性。周四晚上，总统乔·拜登和前总统唐纳德·特朗普将展开首场辩论，届时情况可能会发生变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/ev-chips-crypto-stocks-in-cross-hairs-as-biden-trump-face-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:06:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《世界报》：马克龙将重新任命布雷顿为法国欧盟委员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/macron-to-reappoint-breton-as-french-eu-commissioner-le-monde</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《世界报》援引未透露姓名的知情人士的话称，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙计划重新任命蒂埃里·布雷顿为法国欧盟专员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/macron-to-reappoint-breton-as-french-eu-commissioner-le-monde</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:02:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿莱格拉·斯特拉顿和海伦·钱德勒-怀尔德：末日在望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-27/allegra-stratton-and-helen-chandler-wilde-the-end-is-in-sight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离大选还有七天。根据彭博社的民意调查，保守党支持率小幅下滑至 20.1%，延续了创纪录的低点，工党则轻松领先 20 个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-27/allegra-stratton-and-helen-chandler-wilde-the-end-is-in-sight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:02:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院定于周一发表意见，等待特朗普案的判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-sets-monday-for-opinions-amid-wait-for-trump-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院安排周一为新的意见日 — — 并暗示任期将持续到那之后 — — 法官们将结束本轮审理，本轮审理中包括对唐纳德·特朗普总统争取刑事豁免权的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-sets-monday-for-opinions-amid-wait-for-trump-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:55:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国拒绝联合防务拨款，激怒欧盟领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-irks-eu-leaders-by-opposing-talks-on-how-to-fund-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国正在敦促欧盟领导人放弃有关联合国防开支的措辞，这一立场引发了其他成员国的抵制，他们认为需要额外的资源来提升欧盟的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-irks-eu-leaders-by-opposing-talks-on-how-to-fund-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党雷诺兹称对华政策不应是“二元”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-can-t-have-binary-approach-to-china-labour-s-reynolds-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党一名资深议员敦促谨慎对待中国问题，不要采取二元对立的政策，以此抵制英国国内对华采取严厉措施的政治压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-can-t-have-binary-approach-to-china-labour-s-reynolds-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:38:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着警方调查范围扩大，苏纳克回避内幕赌注问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-police-to-probe-election-bets-in-inside-information-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国大选前，里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 拒绝回答媒体关于保守党陷入赌球丑闻的问题。与此同时，警方正在扩大调查范围，调查首相身边人士是否试图通过押注 7 月 4 日大选时间，利用内幕信息牟利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-police-to-probe-election-bets-in-inside-information-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:28:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲人国民大会撤回贸易提议后南非内阁谈判陷入僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/south-africa-cabinet-talks-stall-after-anc-withdraws-trade-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，南非非洲人国民大会撤回了任命规模较小的民主联盟成员担任贸易和工业部长的提议，此后南非两大政党之间组建内阁的谈判陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/south-africa-cabinet-talks-stall-after-anc-withdraws-trade-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理银行借了巨额债务。现在 1600 万泰晤士水务用户正在买单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thames-water-users-left-to-pick-up-bill-for-former-owner-macquarie</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家澳大利亚集团管理的基金在十年内盈利约 16.5 亿英镑。这家负债累累的英国水务公司目前濒临破产——而下一届政府面临着拯救它的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thames-water-users-left-to-pick-up-bill-for-former-owner-macquarie</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
